ports.behavior:
forward customerNameFromManager
assign DataOrigin.Asia if TRUE from customers
assign DataOrigin.USA if TRUE from customers
assign DataStatus.Regular if TRUE from customers
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if TRUE from customers

forward customerNameFromClerk
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customerNameFromClerk,customers
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customerNameFromClerk,customers
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customerNameFromClerk,customers
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customerNameFromClerk,customers

forward customerName
forward customers
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customerName
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customerName
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customerName
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customers

forward customerName
forward customers
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customerName
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customerName
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customerName
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customers

forward customer
forward customerName
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.USA from customer,customerName
